	<div class=3D"vc_message_box-icon"><i class=3D"fa fa-question"></i>
	</div><h3>How&nbsp;many Pixels&nbsp;are in an Em?</h3>
<p>If base =3D 16 px</p>
<p>1 em&nbsp;=3D 16&nbsp;px</p>
</div>
